snippet.title: ShootRush Release Trailer
snippet.description:
In this endless shooter, your only objectives are to kill as many enemies as you can and to be alive as long as you can ! 

You will have to do some Parkour moves and tricky shots !

Download Link : https://lynox.itch.io/shootrush

Enjoy !
